        array(
            'Type' => 'War',
            'Description' => 'War is sadly one of the more common themes across history. Wars are extreme conflicts that often have little to do with Narrative Conflicts, but instead operate as a backdrop against which the Narrative may take place. Wars place individuals in conflict automatically, which can be a part of a Narrative, or simply be a fact about the world in that Era.',
