            'Rules' => 'Draws and Plays one card as an Ordeal Obstacle, for 1 Stress. Additional Stress will add additional cards (usually between 1 and 3) that increase the Difficulty of this Obstacle. Hazards add triple the current Suspense Level (0-15) as Pips of Difficulty to these Obstacles.',
