            'Description' => 'Playing a card the same suit (wild cards will not count) as a Flush that has a higher Face Value (additional Pips will not count) is called Overtaking a Flush.',
            'Rule' => 'Overtaking a Flush with an over card allows the Player to bury the entire Flush in the Discard Pile immediately. This can be done to any played Flush including an incoming attack.'
