        array(
            'Type' => 'Semi-Grid',
            'Suitable_For' => 'Semi-Grids are intended for improvised complex Ordeals, that include events like dead-end results that require restarting or doubling back. It is especially good for improvising Motional Ordeals.',
            'Description' => 'The Semi-Grid is essentially a Block Spread with some cards "randomly" missing. This limits the ways the Ordeal can be passed through. Yarn-Tellers can remove cards randomly (removing a card on a dice roll of 6 on a d6 for example), or as they see fit. There should be at least one way through the Semi-Grid though.',
