            'Rules' => 'Cast are created from a Power Annex, but may have additional Skills and Talents (usually one per Hitch to a Max of the Power Score (Boon Reduced)). Cast can have a Scale of -3 to +20 based on the Plots involved. Cast may have a Persona and Core Proficiencies rather than a true Personality Annex. They often have at least 3 Hitches (although not compulsory). They usually have I-Ching Hexagrams.',
