        ) , //8
        array(
            'Type' => 'Demon',
            'Description' => 'Demons are created when a Hero has at least one Woe. They can also be called Hobgoblins (Goblins that gain additional Hitches usually, but occasionally Faery-Goblins will also be called Hobs). They may also be created by Increated making a Twisted Pact with a mortal (as this always creates a Woe Hitch). Demons are powerful, able to manipulate the Tapestry around them to their advantage.',
            'Rules' => 'Demons can expend Chi and Twists. They often have multiple Alternates (with perhaps only one Alternate having a Woe). Some Demons (usually Hobgoblins) can steal souls adding them as Alternates.',
            'Min-Hitches' => 4,
            'Max-Hitches' => 8,
            'Woe_Gain' => 'Ruins in Twists when triggered',
            'Hitch_Gain' => 'Marks in Chi / 1 Twist when triggered',
