            'Description' => 'These thresholds indicate talent or 2nd tier membership of a group'
        ) ,
        array(
            'Type' => 'way',
            'Description' => 'These thresholds connect this descendant to that descendant with a direction, as a way that can be travelled, many locations can be placed in a group to create a long road with many locations along it. Ways usually two-way (there and back again), and are considered structural'
        ) ,
        array(
            'Type' => 'window',
            'Description' => 'These thresholds allow some or all senses to be used through them, but they cannot easily be passed through. Window thresholds are usually two-way when physical, but may be one way for magical effects. Windows can be turned into way thresholds to allow passage quite easily (they just need to be big enough and open enough)'
        ) ,
    );
